Z_{1},Z_{2},\ldots
X_{nk}=\sigma_{nk}\cdot Z_{k}
 \frac{\underset{1\leq k\leq r_{n}}{max}\sigma_{nk}^{2}}{s_{n}^{2}}\overset{n\rightarrow\infty}{\longrightarrow}0
\sigma_{nk}^2 =1
s_n^2 = \sum_{k=1}^n \sigma_{nk}^2 = n
 \max_{1 \leq k \leq n } \frac{\sigma^2_k}{s^2_n} \rightarrow 0 \quad \text{as } n \rightarrow + \infty
